<div class="fluid-row" id="header">
<h1 class="title toc-ignore">COVID-19 victims in Israel</h1>
<h4 class="author"><em>Dennis Yaroshevich</em></h4>
<h4 class="date"><em>May 03, 2020, 21:38 GMT+3</em></h4>
</div>
<hr />
<p>There is no official public data about all victims of COVID-19 in Israel.<br />
Ministry of Health publishes daily summary statistics - number of deaths total and per each hospital.<br />
But there is no any additional data about victims.</p>
<p>All detailed data I gather is from news web sites: ynet.co.il and rotter.co.il.<br />
Not all victims were published on media web sites so my data is not complete.<br />
Also some typo errors might be occured during data collection.</p>
